- ✅ Flexibility, low cost, audit-friendly
- ⚠️ Higher risk of manual errors → cần rigorous double-check
- ⚠️ No native multi-user support → single-controller access
- ⚠️ Limited automation → monthly close sẽ tốn nhiều thời gian
- 📋 **Required Templates:** GL, Journal Entries, Trial Balance, AP/AR Aging, Bank Reconciliation, P&L, Balance Sheet, Cash Flow (xem `_TEMPLATES/Excel/`)
{{ENDIF}}

