## 7️⃣ AUTHORIZATION MATRIX (Approval Thresholds)

### Level: **{{APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.PRESET}}**

| Transaction Amount | Approver Required | Notes |
|--------------------|-------------------|-------|
| **< {{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_1_MAX|currency}}** | Staff Accountant / any authorized user | Routine operating expenses |
| **{{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_1_MAX|currency}} – {{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_2_MAX|currency}}** | Manager / Controller | Requires receipt + justification |
| **{{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_2_MAX|currency}} – {{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_3_MAX|currency}}** | CFO (or CEO if no CFO) | Requires supporting documentation + memo |
| **> {{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_3_MAX|currency}}** | CEO / Board of Directors | Requires formal resolution for capital expenditures |

### Additional Controls
- **Dual Approval Required:**
  - Wire transfers >{{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.DUAL_APPROVAL_THRESHOLD|currency}}
  - New vendor setup (prevent fictitious vendors)
  - Changes to Chart of Accounts
  - Payroll changes (new hire, pay rate change, terminations)
- **Capitalization threshold:** Items >{{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.CAPEX_THRESHOLD|currency}} cân nhắc CapEx thay vì expense
- **Segregation of Duties:**
  - Preparer ≠ Approver ≠ Recorder for any journal entry >{{FORMAT:APPROVAL_THRESHOLDS.TIER_1_MAX|currency}}
  - Person who cuts checks ≠ person who reconciles bank
- **Monthly Review:** Controller signs off on all JEs posted in the period before lock

